Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.glassman.GlassmanFR, ['\x01S3333330000002D7',
    '\x01Q51'], ['A', 'R00000000040044'], '\r') as inst:
    set_defaults(inst)
    inst.set_status(voltage=10 * u.kilovolt, current=1.2 * u.milliamp,
        output=True)
    assert inst.output
    assert inst.voltage == 10 * u.kilovolt
    assert inst.current == 1.2 * u.milliamp
